title: you’re not running out of time: overcoming the “fear” of growing up
itunes:title: you’re not running out of time: overcoming the “fear” of growing up
description:
Brooke and Danielle are solo this week and getting deep about growing up and adulthood!  With Danielle graduating in just a few months and Brooke turning 24 in a few months, the gals are talking about the pressures of being at these various points in life.  Brooke and Danielle also catch up on their lives and share some insightful tips and recommendations to implement this week and beyond.
